title: SWAT Model for Cedar Creek - SMA Study
author: Venkatesh Merwade
abstract: This is a calibrated SWAT model for Cedar Creek in Indiana. It was used by Rajib and Merwade (2016) to investigate the role of SCS CN method in soil moisture accounting algorithm in SWAT.
